- Players: Typically 2 — you vs. computer (or another player).
- Choices: Each player picks one of three:
- 🪨 Rock
- 📄 Paper
- ✂️ Scissors
- Winning Logic:
- Rock crushes Scissors 🪨 > ✂️
- Scissors cuts Paper ✂️ > 📄
- Paper covers Rock 📄 > 🪨
- Draw Condition:
- If both players choose the same item, it’s a draw.

